data.description: The search is over! This delightful 4-bed, 3-bath residence features a 3-car garage, extended driveway, convenient RV gate/parking, & a well-maintained front yard. Discover an inviting living room w/ high ceilings, floods of natural light, neutral palette, & plush carpeting. Gather your loved ones in the family room, providing backyard access, 2 balconies, & media niche! The kitchen includes ample cabinet/counter space, built-in appliances, a handy pantry, & a two-tier island w/breakfast bar. The versatile loft w/balcony is ideal for a game area! The main bedroom has private balcony access, an ensuite w/dual sinks, & a walk-in closet. Enjoy fresh air from the balconies, in the front & back! The backyard showcases a covered patio, natural grass, & a citrus tree. Must see! It will sell fast
